WEBVTT

00:00:05.918 --> 00:00:10.384
shoyn, Dov, kumt shoyn UNK hitsert, m'kumt tsum toytes marsh.

00:00:10.525 --> 00:00:19.243
iz eyner tsu aykh tsugekumen un m'hot aykh gezogt az m'darf helfn Robertn, yo? ver iz Robert?

00:00:16.721 --> 00:00:17.360
yo.

00:00:18.692 --> 00:00:21.693
a a a a khaver geven fun Belgye.

00:00:21.693 --> 00:00:24.322
fun diment arbet iz er geven.

00:00:24.852 --> 00:00:31.883
geven a gehat a fabrik fun dimentn, dos heyst geshlifn shteyner. UNK

00:00:32.867 --> 00:00:34.363
tsugekumen,

00:00:34.842 --> 00:00:36.776
ikh hob im unter gehaltn,

00:00:37.373 --> 00:00:40.236
un er iz geblibn lebn.

00:00:40.933 --> 00:00:41.787
yo.

00:00:42.418 --> 00:00:43.796
bin geven

00:00:44.359 --> 00:00:47.255
ikh bin geven in poylishn militer.

00:00:48.156 --> 00:00:51.536
dos iz geven a yonkiper, m'iz gegangen di

00:00:51.536 --> 00:00:55.136
bolshevikes hobn undz gehitn biz Varshe.

00:00:55.648 --> 00:00:58.427
nakher m'iz tsurik gegangen.

00:00:58.883 --> 00:01:02.488
kum ikh arayn in a shtetl Augustov.

00:01:02.214 --> 00:01:08.298
dos iz shoyn, dos iz shoyn nokh di milkhome. eyn moment, eyn moment, nokh nokh nisht, nokh nisht.

00:01:04.427 --> 00:01:05.939
nokh di milkhome.

00:01:08.541 --> 00:01:09.685
nokh nisht.

00:01:09.685 --> 00:01:12.332
hitsert, vi lang, dos,

00:01:10.245 --> 00:01:17.613
dos iz, dos iz geven ven ikh bin geven in poylishn militer, in tsvontsikstn yor.

00:01:16.945 --> 00:01:20.578
neyn, dos iz nisht vikhtik hitsert, dos iz nisht vikhtik, di poylishe,

00:01:20.578 --> 00:01:22.510
hitsert iz mir vikhtik

00:01:22.510 --> 00:01:28.768
vi lang hot gedoyert, vi lang hot gedoyert der toytes-marsh? vi lang, vifl vifl dort?

00:01:28.842 --> 00:01:30.720
*

00:01:30.720 --> 00:01:36.632
m'hot gegangen di gantse, m'hot ge- di gantse tsayt m'hot nor gegangen un gegangen, yo?

00:01:37.575 --> 00:01:38.727
in di vagonen.

00:01:38.723 --> 00:01:39.810
in di vagonen.

00:01:39.681 --> 00:01:42.824
tsu der arbet UNK,

00:01:41.326 --> 00:01:45.190
neyn, in toytes-marsh, m'redt hitstert fun toytes-marsh.

00:01:45.244 --> 00:01:46.672
toytn-marsh

00:01:46.695 --> 00:01:50.570
hot zikh geendikt, s'iz geven ofn di di tirn,

00:01:51.572 --> 00:01:53.861
nisht geven keyn S. S.

00:01:54.390 --> 00:01:58.400
ikh hob dokh aykh gezogt, ikh bin arop gelofn oyfn KVISH,

00:01:58.727 --> 00:02:02.045
un s'iz geven amerikaner.

00:02:02.389 --> 00:02:04.357
hot men undz nakher

00:02:04.515 --> 00:02:06.162
tsurik geshikt

00:02:06.490 --> 00:02:09.251
in a lager arayn, Feldafing.

00:02:09.246 --> 00:02:16.018
eyn moment, eyn moment, mir veln kumen. in toytes-marsh zenen a sakh yidn gefaln, gesh- geshtorbn?

00:02:15.180 --> 00:02:25.935
a sakh zenen gefaln. undz hobn gemeynt s'iz partizaner, tsum sof hot zikh aroysgevizn az dos iz geven der vos hobn nisht gekent geyn

00:02:25.935 --> 00:02:29.212
a koyl in kop arayn. ze'mir nakher gevoyer.

00:02:27.583 --> 00:02:33.027
ir zent ir zent, dos ales iz geven fun Dakho biz biz vu?

00:02:33.237 --> 00:02:36.828
der toytes-marsh fun Dakho biz gegangen

00:02:36.828 --> 00:02:39.440
di gantse tsayt mit fus gegangen, yo?

00:02:39.936 --> 00:02:49.110
tsu fus, yo. un a sakh sa- a sakh zenen gefaln. ver es hot nisht gekent geyn hobn di daytshn gegebn a koyl,

00:02:40.146 --> 00:02:40.970
tsu fus.

00:02:47.852 --> 00:02:55.236
a koyl in kop arayn. ober undz ho'mir nisht gevust, m'hot gemeynt s'iz partizaner.

00:02:49.146 --> 00:02:50.441
a koyl in kop arayn.

00:02:55.495 --> 00:02:58.088
nakher ze'mir gevoyer gevorn

00:02:58.296 --> 00:03:02.762
un dan, un nokh eyder Robert, ikh hob unter gehaltn

00:03:03.257 --> 00:03:07.301
iz kumen tsu mir a khaver, alts fun di lager khaveyrim,

00:03:07.341 --> 00:03:09.883
er lebt nokh eyner, in do,

00:03:10.277 --> 00:03:12.684
in in Khayfa.

00:03:13.956 --> 00:03:16.228
iz gekumen eyner tsu mir,

00:03:16.268 --> 00:03:18.197
zogt er, Robert

00:03:18.197 --> 00:03:20.413
vil zikh avek zetsn, muz men,

00:03:19.508 --> 00:03:26.066
yo shoyn, dos hot ir, dos hot ir shoyn dertseylt. nokh dem toytes-marsh

00:03:26.123 --> 00:03:34.385
hot ir geba- ba- bafrayt fun dos, fun bay di amerikaner, vos hobn di amerikaner mit aykh gemakht?

00:03:30.236 --> 00:03:31.787
fun di amerikaner.

00:03:34.775 --> 00:03:36.340
zey hobn gornisht gemakht.

00:03:36.089 --> 00:03:38.300
hobn avek geshikt in a lager?

00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:39.860
m'hot arayn geshikt in a lager,

00:03:39.838 --> 00:03:41.236
vos a lager?

00:03:41.222 --> 00:03:43.801
Feldafing hot es geheysn.

00:03:43.087 --> 00:03:46.924
ir ir ir gedenkt vos a nomen di lager hot?

00:03:47.506 --> 00:03:50.619
ikh ken nisht ales gedenken, vos,

00:03:49.021 --> 00:03:50.551
vos vos ir gedenkt.

00:03:51.216 --> 00:03:53.119
dortn hot men nakher

00:03:53.119 --> 00:03:54.855
m'hot gekrign esn,

00:03:54.878 --> 00:03:59.715
un un tsvey parshoyn oyf a koldre iz geven yo,

00:04:00.008 --> 00:04:02.651
nakher hot men undz tsuzamen genumen,

00:04:02.708 --> 00:04:05.177
yederer fun zayn gegnt,

00:04:05.177 --> 00:04:08.037
ikh nokh Belgye bin tsurik geforn.

00:04:09.103 --> 00:04:14.581
in Belgye tsurik geforn, ober ikh hob nokh shoyn gevust in lager, in Oshvits,

00:04:14.706 --> 00:04:17.467
az mayn froy lebt nisht mit di kinder.

00:04:18.115 --> 00:04:25.298
ir hot gevust un vos iz mitn foter un muter hot ir oykh gevust vos hot pasirt. UNK

00:04:22.654 --> 00:04:26.175
s'iz dokh geven shoyn friert in Poyln, in Varshe.

00:04:27.801 --> 00:04:29.786
bin ikh tsurik gekumen,

00:04:30.012 --> 00:04:32.571
in dortn vu ikh hob gevoynt,

00:04:32.593 --> 00:04:35.607
bin ikh gegangen tsu eyner,

00:04:35.614 --> 00:04:40.437
tsu a yidisher, vos iz geven bahaltn, a sakh yidn zenen geven bahaltn.

00:04:40.437 --> 00:04:42.678
vayl di belger zenen nisht geven

00:04:42.685 --> 00:04:46.391
keyn antisemitn, zey hobn nisht lib gehat dem doytsh.

00:04:46.592 --> 00:04:48.238
hobn zey bahaltn di yidn.

00:04:48.291 --> 00:04:48.833
yo.

00:04:48.833 --> 00:04:51.471
bin ikh gegangen tsu a, tsu m'hot gezogt

00:04:51.679 --> 00:04:55.588
do voynt a poylisher, er hot nisht gezogt a yid JUIF.

00:04:55.881 --> 00:04:58.406
in frantseyzish heyst dos JUIF.

00:04:58.716 --> 00:05:01.058
nor do iz voynt a POLONAIS.

00:05:01.058 --> 00:05:04.717
zi iz gegangen mit mir, s'geven eyne a shokhnte.

00:05:05.095 --> 00:05:08.348
nu, bin ikh geshlofn eyn nakht dortn,

00:05:08.348 --> 00:05:10.590
un mit der man, mit dos,

00:05:10.630 --> 00:05:14.741
bin ikh gegangen fun di politsey ahin zikh meldn.

00:05:15.068 --> 00:05:18.591
kum arayn un du veyst dokh in politsey in der fri

00:05:18.591 --> 00:05:22.891
iz do yeder hot farshidene gesheftn bay di fentsterlekh.

00:05:23.252 --> 00:05:25.558
ikh kum tsu tsu fentstern,

00:05:25.699 --> 00:05:27.448
gibt der komisar

00:05:27.454 --> 00:05:29.304
a geshrey, "Berek!"

00:05:30.340 --> 00:05:32.528
er hot geheysn ale aheym geyn,

00:05:32.753 --> 00:05:35.109
un mikh arayn gerufn.

00:05:35.318 --> 00:05:38.906
"gey, kumts an andert mol," tsu zey hot er gezogt.

00:05:39.182 --> 00:05:40.408
zey hobn gevolt,

00:05:40.853 --> 00:05:44.511
er hot UNK oysgefregt zikh, zogt er zest,

00:05:44.511 --> 00:05:48.047
bizn letstn tog hot dayn froy gekrign

00:05:48.047 --> 00:05:50.516
untershtitsungen fun undz.

00:05:50.674 --> 00:05:55.098
ikh hob im dertseylt vi azoy s'iz tsugegangen dos lebn mayns.

00:05:58.302 --> 00:06:01.249
hob ikh im gezogt, "efsher konstu

00:06:01.423 --> 00:06:04.694
shafn a voynung? ikh hob nisht vu tsu shlofn.

00:06:04.694 --> 00:06:06.294
baym porfolk ken men,"

00:06:06.486 --> 00:06:08.387
zogt er, "gut ikh vel zukhn."

00:06:08.410 --> 00:06:10.969
dervayl hob ikh getrogn a tshekher,

00:06:11.548 --> 00:06:12.827
zogt er,

00:06:12.827 --> 00:06:15.907
Robe- vi hot er geheysn, ikh gedenk shoyn nisht.

00:06:15.907 --> 00:06:17.026
a tshekher.

00:06:17.539 --> 00:06:19.321
a a a shokhn.

00:06:19.615 --> 00:06:24.919
zog ikh, efsher iz do bay dir dortn a tsimer, a a bet?

00:06:24.919 --> 00:06:25.498
yo.

00:06:25.504 --> 00:06:27.472
zogt er, yo, s'do.

00:06:28.137 --> 00:06:34.881
bin ikh gegangen nokh di politsey un ikh hob gezogt im UNK dem komisar az ikh hob shoyn a voynung,

00:06:35.629 --> 00:06:37.091
bay Robe,

00:06:37.131 --> 00:06:40.275
vi hot er geheysn dort? ikh gedenk nisht dem nomen.

00:06:40.275 --> 00:06:43.979
er hot gevust, vayl dortn iz geven a hoyz fun der dos.

00:06:45.147 --> 00:06:48.721
hot im, shoyn. hob ikh im ales dertseylt,

00:06:48.721 --> 00:06:53.066
vi azoy s'iz geven mit mayn froy iz gevorn unter geshtitst.

00:06:53.066 --> 00:06:55.519
dan hot er mikh bald geshikt

00:06:55.660 --> 00:06:57.544
azoy vi sotsyale,

00:06:57.567 --> 00:07:05.509
gegebn tsvey hundert ts- zlo- dos vi azoy heyst es, sh- frantsoy- bel-

00:07:02.100 --> 00:07:05.425
fra- frankishe belgishe franken.

00:07:05.734 --> 00:07:06.850
franken.

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:08.782
mir gegebn.

00:07:09.008 --> 00:07:11.752
gegangen in yidishn komitet arayn,

00:07:12.197 --> 00:07:14.321
oykhet mir gegebn,

00:07:14.193 --> 00:07:16.708
dos iz geven in Antverpn?

00:07:14.391 --> 00:07:15.975
kleydung,

00:07:16.708 --> 00:07:19.488
in velkhe shtot iz dos geven?

00:07:16.749 --> 00:07:17.534
vos?

00:07:19.528 --> 00:07:21.722
dos iz geven in CHARLEROI.

00:07:21.219 --> 00:07:23.231
ah CHARLEROI, yo.

00:07:23.638 --> 00:07:27.142
bin gegangen dortn un mayne khaveyrim oykhet,

00:07:27.570 --> 00:07:30.584
zogt a khaver tsu mir, ikh bin gekumen in shtub arayn,

00:07:31.097 --> 00:07:32.643
zogt er tsu mir,

00:07:32.751 --> 00:07:36.424
hostu noytik gelt? zog ikh, neyn, ikh hob nisht keyn vesh.

00:07:36.497 --> 00:07:39.950
er iz gegangen er hot, vayl ikh hob gelt, m'hot mir gegebn.

00:07:40.632 --> 00:07:42.685
hot men gegebn vesh,

00:07:42.724 --> 00:07:43.460
shoyn,

00:07:43.703 --> 00:07:46.076
mir zol mir nokh gehaltn gut,

00:07:46.673 --> 00:07:47.814
gut, zen,

00:07:47.905 --> 00:07:53.014
nisht, mit a por yor tsi do iz a gantse khevre fun der zelbe shtot!

00:07:53.014 --> 00:07:56.488
khaveyrim in Khayfe vos zey voynen.

00:07:57.692 --> 00:07:59.272
oh!

00:07:59.515 --> 00:08:02.889
ikh bin gegangen fun Poyln, ikh red, ikh red dokh tsurik

00:08:02.897 --> 00:08:05.515
neyn nisht tsurik UNK.

00:08:04.537 --> 00:08:09.364
neyn, ikh vil redn dertseyln aykh a vikhtike zakh.

00:08:09.488 --> 00:08:11.822
ikh bin geven in poylishn militer,

00:08:11.822 --> 00:08:13.281
m'hot undz geyogt,

00:08:13.281 --> 00:08:17.649
nakher tsurik geyogt, un hot men gekrign hilf fun Frankraykh

00:08:17.689 --> 00:08:19.449
in a yomkiper,

00:08:19.449 --> 00:08:24.787
ikh hob gehat tsvey ferd, s'iz aza a in tabor geven.

00:08:24.996 --> 00:08:26.812
gehat tsvey ferd,

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:31.048
ikh bin arayngekumen in a shtetl arayn, August dorf,

00:08:31.273 --> 00:08:34.102
nisht vayt fun Byalistok iz es.

00:08:36.419 --> 00:08:39.028
ikh bin arayn, bin ikh arayn in a shtub.

00:08:39.154 --> 00:08:40.785
yomkiper iz es geven.

00:08:41.618 --> 00:08:43.935
a malekh hot mikh arayn geshtupt.

00:08:43.935 --> 00:08:47.551
shteyt a froy mit a kind, mit a ⟨mamkele⟩,

00:08:47.828 --> 00:08:50.977
zi vart oyf eynem m'zol helfn.

00:08:52.097 --> 00:08:53.981
zog ikh, tsi hobn vaser?

00:08:54.544 --> 00:08:55.820
zogt zi, neyn.

00:08:55.843 --> 00:08:57.524
gebn zey mir a nem,

00:08:57.615 --> 00:09:02.385
gey a nem arayn genug.

00:09:02.610 --> 00:09:08.746
hob ikh o- ikh bin gegangen ontsindn, zogt zi, m'tor nisht, s'iz yomkiper! zog ikh, ikh meg.

00:09:08.989 --> 00:09:10.755
ongetsundn,

00:09:11.166 --> 00:09:13.669
ikh hob ir gegebn broyt vays,

00:09:13.669 --> 00:09:15.786
undz ho'mir gekrign vays broyt,

00:09:15.786 --> 00:09:18.011
ikh hob ir gegebn tsuker,

00:09:18.152 --> 00:09:20.525
zi hot gegebn brokhes,

00:09:21.257 --> 00:09:23.431
nokh dos iz a mazl,

00:09:23.431 --> 00:09:26.061
a malekh hot mikh geshikt hilf.

00:09:26.083 --> 00:09:28.583
dos nem- ken ikh keyn mol nisht far-

